tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE PatientFeedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  satisfaction_rating INT,
  visit_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE PatientFeedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  rating INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE QualityImprovement (
  improvement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  feedback_id INT,
  survey_id INT,
  service_id INT,
  improvement_text TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE PatientFeedback (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    survey_date DATE,
    satisfaction_score INT,
    feedback_text TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE SurveyResponse (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    question_id INT,
    patient_id INT,
    response_value TEXT
);
